CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

October 7, 2008

[Cite as 10/07/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-5207.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2008-0314. Cundall v. U.S. Bank, N.A.

Hamilton App. Nos. C-070081 and C-070082, 174 Ohio App.3d 421, 2007-0hio-7067. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County. Upon consideration of appellees’ motion to file Volume II of the second supplement under seal,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
